name: historical-shoreline-for-louisiana-geographic-nad83-noaa-2001-shoreline-la-noaa-1986
notes: These data were automated to provide a suitable geographic information system (GIS) data layer depicting the historical shoreline for Louisiana. These data are derived from shoreline maps that were produced by the NOAA National Ocean Service including its predecessor agencies.
